strings.Value: "And I like Bokken. He reminds me of a book seller I know... Cold and tart at first, but if he likes someone, it's forever."
"It was so good of Oleg and Svetlana to help him. I think he'd have a tough time without them."
"Many girls are like that, ha, ha."
"Of course, one must make allowances for his age. But he'd be better off if he learned some manners."
